# This directory holds server-side secrets that are NEVER committed to git.
#
# For the Earth Engine tier (OPENET_MODE=gee), place the Google service-account
# JSON key here as: gee-key.json
# docker-compose.yml mounts this directory read-only at /run/secrets, so the key
# is available to the app at /run/secrets/gee-key.json.
#
# See docs/earth-engine-tier-setup.md. Everything in this folder except this
# .gitkeep file is gitignored.
